  m_text: 'Elements:

    Each card has a specific element it is attuned to, these
    elements are: terror(gray), bliss(yellow), Misery(blue) and wrath(red). all enemies
    are also attuned to an element that they enbody, attacking them with that element
    will cause special effects.'
